<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，凯蒂和乔伊坐在餐桌前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂皱着眉头，看着自己面前的碗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得吃麦片吗？” 她问妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷平时都是给他们做燕麦粥或者薄饼的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，宝贝们。” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爷爷不在家，我得准备去上班。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊突然想到了一个好主意！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去拿些鸡蛋做煎蛋卷！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她穿上雨衣，跑向鸡圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好，小鸡们！” 她跟母鸡们打招呼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一打开门，四只鸡就跑到她脚边咯咯地叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把手伸向鸡窝，居然没有鸡蛋！好奇怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“母鸡们太懒了。” 乔伊回到厨房说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天没有鸡蛋！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈在洗碗槽洗碗，她抬起了头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是挺奇怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，反正你们俩现在该去上学了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79829</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>抓紧时间吃你们的麦片。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79830</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有，别忘了放学后来图书馆。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在课上，贝柔老师说今天要准备社会研究课的发表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96627</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在接下来的半个小时里，请自己做作业。” 贝柔老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以上网或看书来查领袖的信息。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拉里拿出一本关于富兰克林·德拉诺·罗斯福总统的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉在读一本关于亚伯拉罕·林肯的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好像大部分同学都去过公共图书馆了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都已经开始准备发表文了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，乔伊还没选好她的领袖！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝柔老师看见了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来，乔伊，看看这个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝柔老师递给她一本叫做《美国伟人传》的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你也许能在这里找到你想写的人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您。” 乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她打开书，开始阅读起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，她无法集中注意力。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在想今天早上妈妈贴在冰箱上的家务清单，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在想自己带了什么午饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她开始想爷爷和爸爸去钓鱼时会做些什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂用了一会儿电脑，突然跳起来，跑向乔伊的书桌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道亚伯拉罕·林肯会为了借一本书而走几英里吗？” 凯蒂小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他热爱阅读和写作。” 凯蒂补充说。乔伊耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以，今天放学后，我们最好走路去图书馆！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明白了吗 ？就像亚伯拉罕·林肯一样！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊看着她的妹妹，叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂，我们反正得走路去那里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。” 凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可我还是要把它写在我的发表里的。哈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她冲回了电脑前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208713</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>放学后，天还在下雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我觉得自己真的像个领袖！” 凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她重重地踩了几下一个结冰的水坑，冰裂开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们穿过冰冷的雨水走路去借书，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我们认为教育很重要！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊翻了个白眼，继续静静地走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在图书馆，妈妈帮乔伊找到了很多关于领袖的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，” 乔伊慢慢地说，“我该写哪位领袖呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以帮你选书，宝贝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，我不能帮你选领袖，你得自己决定。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈拍了拍那堆书，笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你很快就会找到你想写的人的。别担心！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚饭后，乔伊练小提琴练到睡觉时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她拿起一个手电筒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去看看鸡蛋！” 她喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走向外面的鸡圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一、二、三、四、五、六。” 乔伊数了数鸡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“都在！” 然后，她用手电筒照了一下鸡窝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还是没有鸡蛋！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>